    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal as a parts car or a major restoration project for a dedicated hobbyist. The engine currently has a severe knock and will likely require a full rebuild or replacement to be reliable. Externally, there is significant structural rust on the frame and lower body panels, and the paint is heavily oxidized. The interior shows heavy wear with several tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please note that this car is being sold strictly as-is and will need to be towed.",
