    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has been really well-loved and maintained. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make its next owner very happy. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
