    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a broad powerband. This chassis is sorted, equipped with a limited-slip variable M differential and reinforced subframe for superior torsional rigidity. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS refresh and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain operates with factory precision. The suspension maintains excellent damping characteristics, providing a communicative steering rack and neutral handling. A well-sorted example of a modern classic, balanced for both spirited canyon carving and daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
