      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper reflect its honest road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows only light, natural creasing, and every electronic feature and safety sensor functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is robust\u2014having recently undergone a comprehensive inspection and fresh oil service. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires have significant tread life remaining. This is a reliable, well-cared-for example that perfectly balances high-end performance with everyday practicality, ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence.",
      "price": 36800.0,
